summary: Animal Eyes | T - 1/1  There are monsters in the forest, Child   Creatures in the dark    And if they catch ahold of you   ...
caption:
Animal Eyes | T - 1/1

There are monsters in the forest, Child  
Creatures in the dark  
And if they catch ahold of you  
They’ll steal your beating heart

Beware their yellow eyes, my Dear  
For malice they conceal  
They’ll dig their claws inside your mind  
Confusing what is real

To join your souls is their desire  
For they are oft alone  
They’ll slice your ribs and crawl inside  
And make of you a home

body:
Guys Starkiller Base is basically a less portable option to the Sun Crusher from Legends.

Both use the power of a star to demolish whole star systems at a time. Same principle, only the Crusher was designed to flight in and out of a system after supernovaing a sun.
